description:
Expose milestones in GraphQL  for `GroupType`.    

That would allow us to do the following kind of query:  

```
{
  group(fullPath: "gitlab-org") {
    milestones {
    title
    ....
  }
}
```


### Important
We need to be able to filter milestones between a `start_date` and `end_date`.
This is part of the work that needs to be done for https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/issues/6802.
